-- ExitProcess
.hn2_2: PUT .pe 1986 69
.hn2_3: PUT .pe 1987 120
.hn2_4: PUT .pe 1988 105
.hn2_5: PUT .pe 1989 116
.hn2_6: PUT .pe 1990 80
.hn2_7: PUT .pe 1991 114
